%p Hello,

%p
  You have been added to the group
  = "'#{@group.display_name}'"
  at Kuusi Palaa.

- unless @group.description.blank?
  %p
    Group description:
    %br/
    = @group.description
%p
  Groups are a new feature that allows users to group together to represent projects, organisations or other matter. Groups are able to collectively own stakes in Kuusi Palaa.

%p
  If you have been added to this group against your will, you may leave via the
  = link_to 'membership page', 'https://kuusipalaa.fi/members'
  = "."



%p
  If you don't want to receive any emails from Kuusi Palaa at all, you can unsubscribe from notifications from your
  = link_to 'user profile page', edit_user_url(@user)
  = "."
  If you do want to receive these emails, make sure admin@temporary.fi is whitelisted in your email client.

%p Thank you for your interest in Kuusi Palaa.
